edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.ideal.simplify

Class BoundMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.ideal.simplify.BoundMap

  • public class BoundMap
extends java.lang.Object
    A BoundMap keeps track of bounds on all Monic expressions occurring within a given simplification context. It has state: as more information is learned about those expressions, methods are called in this class which refines the bounds. There is one instance of BoundMap associated to each IdealSimplifier.
